tp://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, she hasannounced her retirementfrom competitive breaking.\", \"from\": 413, \"to\": 475, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"September 4, 2024:Speaking to Australia's Channel 10 TV, Gunn said actually it was ignorance of the sport which motivated people to dunk on her so.\", \"from\": 477, \"to\": 624, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 507, \"end\": 516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9950598990058512, \"rank\": 0.0024739823607729384, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 519, \"end\": 529, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Network_10\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7113732134107645e-20, \"text\": \"Channel 10\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Network_10\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Network_10\"}, {\"begin\": 530, \"end\": 532, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television\", \"score\": 0.9329678741485307, \"rank\": 0.03172472910701649, \"text\": \"TV\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television\"}, {\"begin\": 534, \"end\": 538, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9999580197408113, \"rank\": 3.91938450220131e-05, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was really sad how much hate that it did evoke,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 687, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And a lot of the responses is also just due to people not being very familiar with breaking and the diversity of approaches in breaking.\\\"\", \"from\": 688, \"to\": 826, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She described the vitriol levied against her as \\\"alarming,\\\" and maintained that she is in fact the best B girl in Australia.\", \"from\": 827, \"to\": 951, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 941, \"end\": 950, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9950598990058512, \"rank\": 0.0024739823607729384, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think my record speaks to that,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 997, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was the top-ranked Australian B girl in 2020 and 2022, and 2023.\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1065, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1020, \"end\": 1030, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9968830837036841, \"rank\": 0.0019904004448198735, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u2026 So the record is there, but anything can happen in a battle.\\\"\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1129, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Anything \\u2026like T-Rex arms?\", \"from\": 1130, \"to\": 1156, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Raygun said she was sorry for the backlash the community has experienced.\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1231, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Unfortunately, we just need some more resources in Australia for us to have a chance to be world champions,\\\" she said, adding that she'd trained all year for the Olympics: \\\"I have really put my body through it, put my mind through it.\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1467, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1284, \"end\": 1293, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9950598990058512, \"rank\": 0.0024739823607729384, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But if that's not good enough for someone, what can I say?\\\"\", \"from\": 1468, \"to\": 1527, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"November 6, 2024:Rachael Gunn has announced her official retirement from the sport of breaking.\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1624, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1546, \"end\": 1553, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"score\": 0.9999990454148255, \"rank\": 8.092331684351254e-07, \"text\": \"Rachael\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\"}, {\"begin\": 1554, \"end\": 1558, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9999580197408113, \"rank\": 3.91938450220131e-05, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was going to keep competing, for sure, but that seems really difficult for me to do now,\\\" she told Australian radio station 2DayFM, as reported by theBBC.\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1782, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1727, \"end\": 1737, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9968830837036841, \"rank\": 0.0019904004448198735, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think the level of scrutiny that's going to be there, and people will be filming it, and it will go online.\\\"\", \"from\": 1783, \"to\": 1894, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn says the backlash against her, which included everything from threats of violence to a Rachel Dratch, have made dancing in general less fun.\", \"from\": 1895, \"to\": 2040, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1895, \"end\": 1899, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9999580197408113, \"rank\": 3.91938450220131e-05, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 1987, \"end\": 2000, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachel_Dratch\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rachel Dratch\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachel_Dratch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachel_Dratch\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Dancing is so much fun, and it makes you feel good.\", \"from\": 2041, \"to\": 2093, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not think people should feel crap about the way that they dance,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2094, \"to\": 2174, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I still dance, and I still break.\", \"from\": 2175, \"to\": 2209, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But, you know, that's like in my living room with my partner!\\\"\", \"from\": 2210, \"to\": 2272, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Things you buy through our links may earnVox Mediaa commission.\", \"from\": 2274, \"to\": 2337, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Have an Account?\", \"from\": 2379, \"to\": 2395, \"entities\": []}]}"